title: "Research OS"
abstract: "Research OS is an MCP server that hosts grounded research-data-management, reproducibility, and FAIR-data protocols for AI coding assistants. It scaffolds a versioned research workspace, drives audited multi-step analyses, and emits citation-ready, share-safe deliverables."
